Carmine Caridi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carmine_Caridi 0 Carmine Caridi (born 23 January 1934) is an American television and film actor. He has appeared in a wide variety of roles over the past 30 years. He lives in West Hollywood. In 2004, he became the first person to be expelled from the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences.
